Description: Linux control center for Acer Predator and Nitro laptops
 ASense is a native control panel for supported Acer laptops. It provides
 firmware performance profiles, fan control, live hardware telemetry,
 keyboard and chassis lighting, and selected battery and platform settings.
 .
 Hardware features are detected independently through Linux platform-profile,
 hwmon, Acer WMI and supported HID interfaces. The package includes a
 privileged, socket-activated daemon and an ASense DKMS module.
